CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Venu is an entertainment and hospitality holding company based in Colorado Springs, Colorado. Venu designs, develops, owns, and operates (whether directly or through third-party operators) up-scale music venues, outdoor amphitheaters, and full-service restaurants and bars where music, dining, and luxury experiences converge. Currently, Venu operates two indoor venues, three restaurants, and one outdoor amphitheater across Colorado and Georgia.
